data.description: Spacious log home, perfect for those seeking self-sufficiency & tranquility in the foothills of Northern Colorado. Remarkable end-of-the-road, 15.5-acre property offers beautiful views, stunning rock-outcroppings & a blend of sustainable living & mainstream comfort! Owned solar panels provide total off grid living however you're on the grid w/ a flip of a switch. Main features are a warm, inviting large living room w/ T & G ceiling & pellet stove, kitchen w/ ample storage, pantry, mud room & laundry. 3 upper bedrooms are sunny & bright.  2 covered decks make for a great place to enjoy the scenery & relax, not to mention there are 2 Hot tubs, a steam sauna & new walk-in tub!  There's plenty of space in the oversized garage, shop & storage room. Property is served by 2 propane tanks, propane boiler, an outdoor woodburning boiler heats the greenhouse, a water well w/ 1500-gal in reserve, a full septic system & a wide range of outbuildings too, including a 16 X 24 heated greenhouse, 10 x20 improved shed w/loft, full-service RV site, bath house, cedar barn with 4 stalls & 4 corrals/gated pens, plus more! Located in beautiful Green Mountain Meadows community, which includes road maintenance & easy access year-round. Please see brochure for additional features.
